      "title": "Angular Momentum: Understanding Spatial Aspects in Chemistry and Physics",
      "abstract": "Angular Momentum Operators and Wave Functions. Coupling of Two Angular Momentum Vectors. Transformation under Rotation. The Coupling of More than Two Angular Momentum Vectors. Spherical Tensor Operators. Energy-level Structure and Wave Functions of a Rigid Rotor. Appendix: Computer Programs for 3J, 6J, and 9J Symbols. Index."
